{"word":"ἀκριβῶς","slug":"ἀκριβῶς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀϰριβῶς</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀκριβής\">ἀκριβής</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b><i>diligently, carefully</i> <a href='B:470 2:8'>Mt 2:8</a></b> (Herod had the magi ‘pin-point’ the time), <b><a href='B:490 1:3'>Lk 1:3</a>; <a href='B:510 18:25'>Ac 18:25</a>;</b> <el>βλέπετε <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὖν\">οὖν</a> ἀ.</el> <i>so pay careful attention</i> <b><a href='B:560 5:15'>Eph 5:15</a>;</b> <el>ἀ. οἴδατε</el> <i>you well know</i> <b><a href='B:590 5:2'>1 Th 5:2</a>.</b> Comp. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀκριβέστερον\">ἀκριβέστερον</a></el> <i>in more detail</i> <b><a href='B:510 18:26'>Ac 18:26</a>; <a href='B:510 23:15'>23:15</a>; <a href='B:510 24:22'>24:22</a></b> (Felix was well informed). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀκριβόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀκρίς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}